description:
This is a Ubuntu Server 12.04 LTS Virtual Box Image (http://VirtualBoxImages.com/GettingStarted)

for using the open source content management system Contao-3.0.3 &lt;a href=&quot;
https://contao.org/en/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
https://contao.org/en/&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;
https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Contao&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Contao&lt;/a&gt;

you can reach the Contao admin section over http://__VirtualMachineIpAddress__/contao/contao

Ubuntu Server 12.04 LTS (login=ubuntu pw=reverse) 
MySQL (login=root pw=reverse) 
Contao (login=ubuntu pw=reverse ContaoInsallPW: contaoreverse)


the Contao root folder is reachable over:

SSH - ssh://ubuntu@__VirtualMachineIpAddress__/var/www/contao
FTP - ftp://ubuntu@__VirtualMachineIpAddress__/var/www/contao
SMB - smb://ubuntu@__VirtualMachineIpAddress__

if you want to install extension for Contao  &lt;a href=&quot;
http://__VirtualMachineIpAddress__/contao/contao/main.php?do=repository_manager&amp;install=extension&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://__VirtualMachineIpAddress__/contao/contao/main.php?do=repository_manager&amp;install=extension&lt;/a&gt;

you will find a list here &lt;a href=&quot;
http://de.contaowiki.org/Kategorie:Extensions&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://de.contaowiki.org/Kategorie:Extensions&lt;/a&gt;



If you want to use Contao in your group/LAN, change the network mode to &quot;Bridge Mode&quot; here:  
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://media.cdn.ubuntu-de.org/wiki/attachments/39/03/Bildschirmfoto_am_2012-01-18_220315.png&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://media.cdn.ubuntu-de.org/wiki/attachments/39/03/Bildschirmfoto_am_2012-01-18_220315.png&lt;/a&gt;

If you have done this, you need to connect all services over localhost and the ports you chose in the VirtualBox config.

i.e.:  &lt;a href=&quot;
http://127.0.0.1:8080&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://127.0.0.1:8080&lt;/a&gt;
ssh://127.0.0.1:2222  &lt;a href=&quot;
ftp://127.0.0.1:212&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
ftp://127.0.0.1:212&lt;/a&gt;

Plz help seed

- Peponi -
